    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This example features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The VANOS solenoid and seals have been overhauled to maintain peak torque delivery across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Critical subframe reinforcement has been performed to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with refreshed bushings and dampers, while the individual throttle bodies provide immediate throttle response. Though the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system integrity and valve clearances\u2014are within tight tolerances. A mechanically sound platform for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
