    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes an excellent balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the driver-side door handle\u2014standard signs of careful road use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only very slight curb rash on the rear passenger side. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the leather seats show light bolster wear but remain supple and free of any punctures or stains. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment screen and heated seats, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers consistent power, supported by a comprehensive service log showing on-time oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the car tracks straight and true on the highway. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a clean title, offering a reliable and premium driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
