    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me through every commute and weekend trip. It looks great and runs even better\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable set of wheels without that 'brand new' price tag. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
