    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical assembly is robust, with a recently serviced VANOS system and verified valve clearances ensuring optimal timing and compression. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, mitigating the platform's known harmonic stress issues. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and exit speed. While the aesthetics show honest patina from enthusiast use, the suspension kinematics remain tight, and the engine\u2019s power band is as linear and visceral as ever.",
